<i>noun</i>: 허식 [허식], 허세 [허세], 과시 [과ː시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허식 [허식]</dt><br>
<dd>ostentation; vanity</dd><br>
<dd>실속이 없이 겉만 꾸밈.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making something outwardly showy without any substance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허세 [허세]</dt><br>
<dd>bluff; brag; ostentation</dd><br>
<dd>실속이 없이 겉으로만 부풀려 보이는 기세.</dd><br>
<dd>One's spirit that looks higher than it actually is, without substance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>과시 [과ː시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. display</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 능력이나 솜씨 등을 자랑스럽게 드러냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of showing off one's ability or skill boastfully.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ostentation; display</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 힘이나 의지 등을 사실보다 과장하여 드러냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of showing off one's power or will in an exaggerated way.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>